longBusinessSummary: Banco BMG S.A. provides commercial and credit, financing, and investment products and services primarily in Brazil. It operates in two segments, Retail Banking and Wholesale Banking. The company offers digital accounts; payroll, digital account, benefit, and other credit cards; payroll and personal loan, and loan with guarantee; insurance products, including lender, life, and FGTS protected insurance; and Bmg chip, as well as digital banking services. It also provides investment products, such as bank deposit certificates, agribusiness letter of credit, and letters of real estate credit. The company was formerly known as BMG Financeira S.A.Crédito, Financiamento e Investimento and changed its name to Banco BMG S.A. in April 1989. Banco BMG S.A. was founded in 1930 and is headquartered in São Paulo, Brazil. Banco BMG S.A. operates as a subsidiary of Grupo BMG S.A.
